videos.headline: Thompson makes 40-yard Utah TD reception
videos.description: Bryan Thompson reaches out and catches a pass in stride to score a 40-yard touchdown to give Utah a 14-0 lead over Cal.

videos.headline: Moss plows his way to Utah TD
videos.description: Utah takes a 7-0 lead over Cal as Zack Moss plows his way into the end zone to score a four-yard touchdown.
